 one too....but basically because I didnt have anything more productive to do.<br><br>FF 8(PSX)-Great graphics, decent system. OMFG Horrible plot. Absolutely rank. Played up til the last dungeon before my motivation evaporated.<br><br>FF 9....FF 10.....havent decided to buy a PS2, and considering the last 2 FFs for playstation, I think I'm not missing anything ground breaking. I may just be a nostalgist, but I really do miss the themes of the older Final Fantasies. All the techno stuff....swords that are guns....flying steam powered ships.....granted, most of that appeared in all the games, but now the whole techno theme in FFs makes them seem farther away from their roots.<br><br>Hey, cool lunch time! I can leave work! <p>Nenjin Darkeyes<BR>55th lvl Blackguard Xegony<BR>"Dont open your eyes, you wont like what you see. The devil's of Truth steal the souls of the free."--Trent Reznor</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udainbornhald.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dain Bornhald</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/8/02 11:22:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7092.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much do you love FF?</span><hr size=1> You left off 7... how could you forget 7... unless you weren't a true fan!  Heathen!  Burrnnnn!  Burn the heathen!<br><br>/Fir3 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubuuhern.showPublicProfile?language=EN>BUUhern</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/8/02 11:27:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseoutsidenorrath.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?top